author: wn.com
title: Obama says Clinton email server a 'mistake', but denies national security jeopardized
text: President Barack Obama said Sunday that Hillary Clinton's use of a private e-mail server to conduct her correspondence while secretary of state was a "mistake", but denied that U.S. national security had been jeopardized as a result. ...
